reorient_rel

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
reorient_rel -  This method takes in a relative direction and reorients us in the correct way to go in that direction.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string reorient_rel(string word)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^word%^RESET%^ - the direction to look up
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the real direction
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method takes in a relative direction and reorients us in the correct
way to go in that direction.  This also updates our facing so we are
facing in the specified relative direction.
.EP

